@0 = ~I am sure Mavis would have taken care of you just fine, but the problem is she loves you too much to kill you, Isaac.~
@1 = ~Where did you send her, Caim? Tell me, now.~
@2 = ~You will never find her, and you will never know. The only thing you need to know Isaac, is you never deserved her. Never were worthy. And yet, despite everything I have done her heart remains yours.~
@3 = ~With your death...only with your death, can I hope for that to change. And thus, I will deliver you to the hells that you belong in.~
@4 = ~Still alive? You have not even *tasted* my magic.~
@5 = ~Damn you! If I die here, I shall take you with me!~